This patch has AI generated code.

It fixes these issues:

1.  Fix issue where lib64 libs are inappropriately placed in /usr/lib.
2.  Fix issue where libgcc_1.so* is placed in /usr/lib reducing multislot to unislot.
3.  Fix issue where libLLVM.so* is placed in /usr/lib reducing multislot to unislot.
4.  Fixes issue where relative paths for gcc an LLVM are not preserved for hardcoded RPATHs.

